members.name: Nathan DeLisle
members.title: President
members.bio: I am from Appleton, Wisconsin and came to the University of Minnesota in the fall of 2016. I am majoring in Materials Science and Engineering and plan on minoring in Math. Starting in May 2018, I will be completing a two-semester co-op with Kimberly Clark where I will be assisting with various research projects. I love all things Wisconsin (Bucks, Packers, Brewers), except for the Badgers.
